Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:31.40,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}手を伸ばしてみる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:38.07,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}夢の途中きっといつかまた会えるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:46.23,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}慢步走过回家的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.35,0:00:49.69,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}微风轻轻吹拂着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:54.95,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}闲话家常也异常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:59.91,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}至今依旧一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:03.70,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}我们常常相约等候的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:09.17,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}你可否仍然记得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:17.13,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}现在我心怀强烈的向往
